description._content:
Map of the States of Virginia, North Carolina, South Carolina and Georgia; comprehending the Spanish provinces of East and West Florida; exhibiting the boundaries as fixed by the Treaty of Peace between the United States and the Spanish Dominions.  From The American geography; or, a view of the present situation of the United States of America: containing astronomical geography by Jedidiah Morse. London: printed for John Stockdale, 1792. In addition to the boundary between the United States and Spanish Dominions, the map also shows areas inhabited by Native American tribes.
